headline: A Look At Bio-Techne (TECH) Valuation After Analyst Downgrade And Softer Cash Flow Concerns
summary: Bio-Techne (TECH) is back in focus after a recent analyst downgrade that cited softer organic growth and a weaker free cash flow margin, raising fresh questions about how investors should think about the stock today.
